Package sk.stu.fiit.gui.user.message

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MessageWindow
    Class MessageWindow is used as graphical interface for chat function.
    NewInvitationWindow
    For team invitations in app uses class NewInvitationWindow.
    NewMessageWindow
    Class NewMessageWindow allows logged User to write new messages to users they are allowed to.
    SeeMessageWindow
    In SeeMessageWindow User can see full received Message or TeamInvitation.
